3ot2vc6y" width="468" height="382" alt="How to prepare prawns" title="How to prepare prawns" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Video</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> How to prepare prawns</h3> </a></article><article id="node-4209" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-video node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/videos/techniques/how-prepare-chillies"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <span class="vertical-push-item__icon-overlay"></span> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/technique_images/Preparing%20Chillies_0.png?itok=Sbi6lCd-" width="468" height="382" alt="How to prepare chillies" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Video</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> How to prepare chillies</h3> </a></article><article id="node-5366541" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-video node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/videos/techniques/how-make-microwave-chilli"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <span class="vertical-push-item__icon-overlay"></span> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/technique_images/chili700-395.jpg?itok=W-XZYjHV" width="468" height="382" alt="How to make microwave chilli" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Video</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> How to make microwave chilli</h3> </a></article></div></div></div></aside></div> </section><div id="block-bbcgf-outbrain-outbrain-widget" class="block block-bbcgf-outbrain"><div id="outbrain_widget" data-src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/node/98923" data-ob-template="BBCGoodFood"></div></div><div id="ad-mpu-premium-2-narrow"><div class="ad ad--mpu-premium-2-narrow" id="ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_narrow-89635f430d"><script type="text/javascript">Drupal.GPT.createSlot("ad-manager-ad-mpu_prem